---
title: Bacon, Apple & Caramelized Onion Melts with Cheddar, Monterey Jack & Roasted Potato Wedges
description: We all know bacon makes everything better, especially when it comes to sandwiches, but this chef-approved combination of complementary flavors and textures is a game-changer. Layer sourdough bread with smoky bacon, savory-sweet caramelized onion, sharp cheddar cheese, mellow Monterey Jack, and crunchy, tart apple slices. You know the rest of the drill, you master of melts: pan-fry in butter to golden brown perfection and serve alongside a pile of crispy seasoned potato wedges for one satisfying sando.
